Package: cpsc.gov
Title: CPSC Consumer Product Safety Recall Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for CPSC recall data via SaferProducts.gov REST API.
    Search, list, and retrieve product recall details. Includes LLM context injection via cpsc_context().
